headline: POLY MGM MUSEUM Reaches Milestone of Welcoming 500,000 Visitors
summary: The POLY MGM MUSEUM ("Museum") opened its door in November 2024 and has garnered widespread acclaim for its exceptional cultural heritage allure, reaching the milestone of 500,000 visitors in just three months' time. To celebrate this occasion, Ms. Pansy Ho, Chairperson & Executive Director of MGM China Holdings Limited, honored its 500,000th visitor with a curated gift package today.
